[{"text": "You may not know this,", "start": 15.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but you are celebrating an anniversary with me.", "start": 17.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I'm not married,", "start": 20.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but one year ago today,", "start": 23.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I woke up", "start": 26.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from a month-long coma,", "start": 28.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "following a double lung transplant.", "start": 31.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Crazy, I know. Insane.", "start": 35.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 40.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Six years before that,", "start": 42.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I was starting my career", "start": 45.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as an opera singer in Europe,", "start": 47.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "when I was diagnosed with", "start": 49.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "idiopathic pulmonary hypertension --", "start": 51.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "also known as PH.", "start": 54.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It happens when there's a thickening", "start": 56.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in the pulmonary veins,", "start": 59.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "making the right side of the heart", "start": 61.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "work overtime,", "start": 63.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and causing what I call", "start": 65.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the reverse-Grinch effect.", "start": 67.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "My heart was three-and-a-half sizes", "start": 69.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "too big.", "start": 71.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Physical activity becomes very difficult", "start": 74.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for people with this condition,", "start": 76.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and usually after two to five years,", "start": 79.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "you die.", "start": 82.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I went to see this specialist,", "start": 84.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and she was top-of-the-field", "start": 86.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and told me I had to stop singing.", "start": 88.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "She said, \"Those high notes are going to kill you.\"", "start": 91.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "While she didn't have any medical evidence", "start": 94.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to back up her claim", "start": 96.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that there was a relationship", "start": 98.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "between operatic arias", "start": 100.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and pulmonary hypertension,", "start": 102.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "she was absolutely emphatic", "start": 104.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I was singing my own obituary.", "start": 106.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I was very limited by my condition, physically.", "start": 110.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But I was not limited when I sang,", "start": 113.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and as air came up from my lungs,", "start": 116.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "through my vocal cords", "start": 118.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and passed my lips as sound,", "start": 120.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "it was the closest thing I had ever come", "start": 123.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to transcendence.", "start": 126.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And just because of someone's hunch,", "start": 130.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I wasn't going to give it up.", "start": 132.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Thankfully, I met Reda Girgis,", "start": 135.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "who is dry as toast,", "start": 138.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but he and his team at Johns Hopkins", "start": 140.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "didn't just want me to survive,", "start": 143.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "they wanted me", "start": 145.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to live a meaningful life.", "start": 147.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This meant making trade-offs.", "start": 150.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I come from Colorado.", "start": 153.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It's a mile high,", "start": 155.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I grew up there with my 10 brothers and sisters", "start": 157.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and two adoring parents.", "start": 160.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Well, the altitude exacerbated my symptoms.", "start": 162.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So I moved to Baltimore to be near my doctors", "start": 165.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and enrolled in a conservatory nearby.", "start": 167.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I couldn't walk as much as I used to,", "start": 171.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "so I opted for five-inch heels.", "start": 173.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And I gave up salt,", "start": 176.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I went vegan,", "start": 178.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I started taking huge doses of", "start": 180.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "sildenafil,", "start": 184.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "also known as Viagra.", "start": 186.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 189.33, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "My father and my grandfather were always looking for the newest thing", "start": 195.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in alternative or traditional therapies", "start": 198.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for PH,", "start": 200.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but after six months,", "start": 202.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I couldn't walk up a small hill. I couldn't climb a flight of stairs.", "start": 204.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I could barely stand up", "start": 207.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "without feeling like I was going to faint.", "start": 209.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I had a heart catheterization,", "start": 211.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "where they measure this internal arterial pulmonary pressure,", "start": 213.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "which is supposed to be between 15 and 20.", "start": 216.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Mine was 146.", "start": 219.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I like to do things big,", "start": 222.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and it meant one thing:", "start": 225.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "there is a big gun treatment", "start": 227.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for pulmonary hypertension called Flolan,", "start": 229.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and it's not just a drug;", "start": 232.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "it's a way of life.", "start": 234.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Doctors insert a catheter into your chest,", "start": 236.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "which is attached to a pump", "start": 239.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that weighs about four-and-a-half pounds.", "start": 241.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Every day, 24 hours, that pump is at your side,", "start": 245.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "administering medicine", "start": 248.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "directly to your heart,", "start": 250.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and it's not", "start": 253.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a particularly preferable", "start": 255.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "medicine in many senses.", "start": 258.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This is a list of the side effects:", "start": 260.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "if you eat too much salt,", "start": 263.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "like a peanut butter and jelly sandwich,", "start": 266.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you'll probably end up in the ICU.", "start": 268.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "If you go through a metal detector,", "start": 271.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you'll probably die.", "start": 273.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "If you get a bubble in your medicine --", "start": 275.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "because you have to mix it every morning --", "start": 278.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and it stays in there,", "start": 280.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you probably die.", "start": 282.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "If you run out of medicine, you definitely die.", "start": 284.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "No one wants to go on Flolan.", "start": 287.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But when I needed it,", "start": 289.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "it was a godsend.", "start": 292.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Within a few days, I could walk again.", "start": 296.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Within a few weeks, I was performing,", "start": 299.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and in a few months,", "start": 302.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I debuted at the Kennedy Center.", "start": 304.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The pump was a little bit problematic when performing,", "start": 307.33, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "so I'd attach it to my inner thigh", "start": 311.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with the help of the girdle and an ACE bandage.", "start": 313.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Literally hundreds of elevator rides", "start": 316.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "were spent with me alone", "start": 318.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "stuffing the pump into my Spanx,", "start": 320.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "hoping the doors wouldn't open unexpectedly.", "start": 323.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And the tubing coming out of my chest", "start": 328.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "was a nightmare for costume designers.", "start": 331.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I graduated from graduate school in 2006,", "start": 334.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I got a fellowship to go back to Europe.", "start": 337.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "A few days after arriving,", "start": 340.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I met this wonderful, old conductor", "start": 342.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who started casting me in all of these roles.", "start": 344.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And before long, I was commuting", "start": 346.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "between Budapest, Milan", "start": 348.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and Florence.", "start": 350.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Though I was attached", "start": 352.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to this ugly, unwanted,", "start": 354.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "high-maintenance, mechanical pet,", "start": 356.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "my life was kind of like the happy part in an opera --", "start": 358.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "very complicated,", "start": 361.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but in a good way.", "start": 363.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Then in February", "start": 365.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of 2008,", "start": 368.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "my grandfather passed away.", "start": 370.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "He was a big figure in all of our lives,", "start": 372.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and we loved him very much.", "start": 374.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It certainly didn't prepare me", "start": 378.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for what came next.", "start": 380.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Seven weeks later,", "start": 382.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I got a call from my family.", "start": 384.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "My father had been in a catastrophic car accident,", "start": 387.33, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "and he died.", "start": 391.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "At 24, my death would have been", "start": 394.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "entirely expected.", "start": 396.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But his --", "start": 399.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "well, the only way I can articulate how it felt", "start": 402.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "was that it precipitated", "start": 405.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "my medical decline.", "start": 407.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Against my doctors' and family's wishes,", "start": 410.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I needed to go back for the funeral.", "start": 413.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I had to say goodbye", "start": 415.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in some way, shape or form.", "start": 417.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But soon I was showing signs of right-heart failure,", "start": 420.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I had to return to sea level,", "start": 423.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "doing so knowing", "start": 425.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that I probably would never see my home again.", "start": 427.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I canceled most of my engagements that summer,", "start": 432.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but I had one left in Tel Aviv, so I went.", "start": 435.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "After one performance,", "start": 439.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I could barely drag myself", "start": 441.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from the stage to the taxicab.", "start": 443.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I sat down and felt the blood", "start": 445.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "rush down from my face,", "start": 447.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and in the heat of the desert,", "start": 450.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I was freezing cold.", "start": 453.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "My fingers started turning blue,", "start": 455.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I was like, \"What is going on here?\"", "start": 457.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I heard my heart's valves", "start": 460.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "snapping open and closed.", "start": 462.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "The cab stopped,", "start": 464.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I pulled my body from it", "start": 466.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "feeling each ounce of weight", "start": 468.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as I walked to the elevator.", "start": 470.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I fell through my apartment door", "start": 472.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and crawled to the bathroom", "start": 474.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "where I found my problem:", "start": 476.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I had forgotten to mix in", "start": 478.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the most important part of my medicine.", "start": 480.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I was dying,", "start": 482.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and if I didn't mix that stuff up fast,", "start": 484.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I would never leave that apartment alive.", "start": 486.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I started mixing,", "start": 489.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I felt like everything was going to fall out through one hole or another,", "start": 491.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but I just kept on going.", "start": 494.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Finally, with the last bottle in and the last bubble out,", "start": 496.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I attached the pump to the tubing", "start": 498.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and lay there hoping it would kick in", "start": 500.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "soon enough.", "start": 502.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "If it didn't, I'd probably see my father", "start": 505.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "sooner than I anticipated.", "start": 507.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Thankfully, in a few minutes,", "start": 509.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I saw the signature hive-like rash", "start": 512.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "appear on my legs,", "start": 515.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "which is a side effect of the medication,", "start": 517.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I knew I'd be okay.", "start": 519.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We're not big on fear in my family,", "start": 521.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but I was scared.", "start": 524.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I went back to the States,", "start": 526.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "anticipating I'd return to Europe,", "start": 528.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but the heart catheterization", "start": 530.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "showed that I wasn't going anywhere", "start": 532.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "further that a flight-for-life from Johns Hopkins Hospital.", "start": 535.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I performed here and there,", "start": 537.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but as my condition deteriorated,", "start": 539.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "so did my voice.", "start": 541.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "My doctor wanted me to get on the list for a lung transplant.", "start": 543.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I didn't.", "start": 546.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I had two friends who had recently died", "start": 548.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "months after having very challenging surgeries.", "start": 551.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I knew another young man, though, who had PH", "start": 554.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "who died while waiting for one.", "start": 557.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I wanted to live.", "start": 559.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I thought stem cells were a good option,", "start": 561.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but they hadn't developed to a point", "start": 563.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "where I could take advantage of them yet.", "start": 565.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I officially took a break from singing,", "start": 569.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I went to the Cleveland Clinic", "start": 571.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to be reevaluated", "start": 573.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for the third time in five years, for transplant.", "start": 575.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I was sitting there kind of unenthusiastically talking", "start": 578.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with the head transplant surgeon,", "start": 581.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I asked him if I needed a transplant,", "start": 584.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "what I could do to prepare.", "start": 587.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "He said, \"Be happy.", "start": 589.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "A happy patient", "start": 591.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is a healthy patient.\"", "start": 593.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It was like in one verbal swoop", "start": 596.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "he had channeled my thoughts", "start": 598.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "on life and medicine", "start": 600.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and Confucius.", "start": 602.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I still didn't want a transplant,", "start": 604.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but in a month,", "start": 607.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I was back in the hospital", "start": 609.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with some severely edemic kankles --", "start": 611.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "very attractive.", "start": 614.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And it was right-heart failure.", "start": 617.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I finally decided", "start": 621.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "it was time to take my doctor's advice.", "start": 623.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It was time for me to go to Cleveland", "start": 627.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and to start the agonizing wait", "start": 630.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "for a match.", "start": 633.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But the next morning,", "start": 635.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "while I was still in the hospital,", "start": 637.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I got a telephone call.", "start": 639.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It was my doctor in Cleveland,", "start": 641.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Marie Budev.", "start": 643.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And they had lungs.", "start": 645.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It was a match.", "start": 648.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "They were from Texas.", "start": 650.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And everybody was really happy for me,", "start": 652.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but me.", "start": 655.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Because, despite their problems,", "start": 657.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I had spent my whole life training my lungs,", "start": 659.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I was not particularly enthusiastic", "start": 662.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "about giving them up.", "start": 664.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I flew to Cleveland,", "start": 666.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and my family rushed there", "start": 669.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in hopes that they would meet me", "start": 671.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and say what we knew", "start": 673.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "might be our final goodbye.", "start": 675.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But organs don't wait,", "start": 677.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I went into surgery", "start": 680.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "before I could say goodbye.", "start": 682.33, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "The last thing I remember", "start": 686.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "was lying on a white blanket,", "start": 688.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "telling my surgeon that I needed to see my mother again,", "start": 691.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and to please try and save my voice.", "start": 694.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I fell into this apocalyptic dream world.", "start": 697.33, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "During the thirteen-and-a-half-hour surgery,", "start": 701.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I flatlined twice,", "start": 703.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "40 quarts of blood", "start": 706.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "were infused into my body.", "start": 709.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And in my surgeon's 20-year career,", "start": 711.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "he said it was among the most difficult transplants", "start": 714.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that he's ever performed.", "start": 717.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "They left my chest open for two weeks.", "start": 720.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You could see my over-sized heart", "start": 723.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "beating inside of it.", "start": 726.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I was on a dozen machines", "start": 728.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that were keeping me alive.", "start": 730.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "An infection ravaged my skin.", "start": 732.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I had hoped my voice would be saved,", "start": 740.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but my doctors knew", "start": 743.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that the breathing tubes going down my throat", "start": 745.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "might have already destroyed it.", "start": 747.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "If they stayed in, there was no way I would ever sing again.", "start": 749.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So my doctor got the ENT,", "start": 752.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the top guy at the clinic, to come down", "start": 755.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and give me surgery", "start": 758.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to move the tubes around my voice box.", "start": 760.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "He said it would kill me.", "start": 764.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So my own surgeon performed the procedure", "start": 766.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in a last-ditch attempt to save my voice.", "start": 768.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Though my mom couldn't say goodbye to me", "start": 771.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "before the surgery,", "start": 773.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "she didn't leave my side", "start": 775.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in the months of recovery that followed.", "start": 778.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And if you want an example", "start": 781.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of perseverance,", "start": 783.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "grit and strength", "start": 785.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in a beautiful, little package,", "start": 787.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "it is her.", "start": 790.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "One year ago", "start": 795.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to this very day,", "start": 797.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I woke up.", "start": 800.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I was 95 lbs.", "start": 802.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "There were a dozen tubes", "start": 804.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "coming in and out of my body.", "start": 806.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I couldn't walk, I couldn't talk,", "start": 808.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I couldn't eat, I couldn't move,", "start": 810.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I certainly couldn't sing,", "start": 812.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I couldn't even breathe,", "start": 814.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but when I looked up", "start": 817.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I saw my mother,", "start": 820.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I couldn't help but smile.", "start": 823.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Whether by a Mack truck", "start": 827.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "or by heart failure", "start": 830.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or faulty lungs,", "start": 832.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "death happens.", "start": 834.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But life isn't really just about avoiding death, is it?", "start": 836.33, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "It's about living.", "start": 840.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Medical conditions don't negate the human condition.", "start": 843.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And when people are allowed", "start": 847.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to pursue their passions,", "start": 849.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "doctors will find they have better,", "start": 851.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "happier and healthier patients.", "start": 853.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "My parents were totally stressed out", "start": 855.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "about me going and auditioning", "start": 858.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and traveling and performing all over the place,", "start": 860.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but they knew that it was much better for me to do that", "start": 863.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "than be preoccupied with my own mortality all of the time.", "start": 865.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And I'm so grateful they did.", "start": 869.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This past summer, when I was running and singing", "start": 871.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and dancing and playing with my nieces and my nephews", "start": 874.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and my brothers and my sisters and my mother and my grandmother", "start": 877.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in the Colorado Rockies,", "start": 880.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I couldn't help but think of that doctor", "start": 882.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who told me that I couldn't sing.", "start": 884.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And I wanted to tell her,", "start": 887.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I want to tell you,", "start": 889.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we need to stop letting disease", "start": 892.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "divorce us from our dreams.", "start": 895.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "When we do,", "start": 898.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we will find that patients", "start": 900.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "don't just survive;", "start": 902.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we thrive.", "start": 905.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And some of us", "start": 908.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "might even sing.", "start": 910.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 913.33, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "[Singing: French]", "start": 917.33, "duration": 139.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 1057.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 1059.33, "duration": 6.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 1065.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And I'd like to thank my pianist, Monica Lee.", "start": 1067.33, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 1070.33, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "Thank you so much.", "start": 1075.33, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 1077.33, "duration": 2.0}]